sed 25 tests; formatting, diff, docs-list, and flow-doc validation passed.\nObserved result after fix: Approval scenario selection, redaction, checkpoint command generation, watcher race handling, checkpoint metadata validation, and CLI flag routing all pass their focused tests.\nWhat was not tested: A live Slack/Mantis run against real Slack credentials was not run from this local worktree.\n",
